    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chaotic Party Platforming</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive the joy of classic playground fun in quick and crazy rounds for up to 6 players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/a7ebb7db3e2e7335afba549cd6c8cf7a.poster.avif?t=1770091663\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/a7ebb7db3e2e7335afba549cd6c8cf7a.webm?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/a7ebb7db3e2e7335afba549cd6c8cf7a.mp4?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/d35571be0db3d678a72e01c70147f883.poster.avif?t=1770091663\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/d35571be0db3d678a72e01c70147f883.webm?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/d35571be0db3d678a72e01c70147f883.mp4?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Items and Unlocks for Days</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover over 30 power-ups, weapons, and obstacles that stack and interact in astonishing ways</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock 6 dynamic stages and cute pixel-y characters, each brimming with unique themes and features</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock two extra-secret, extra-wild game modes!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/27730575b7f56aaac12155794a2eb939.poster.avif?t=1770091663\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/27730575b7f56aaac12155794a2eb939.webm?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/27730575b7f56aaac12155794a2eb939.mp4?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Precise, Frantic Controls</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swipe at just the right moment to tag your foes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wall jump, platform, and grab items to outrun and outplay everyone</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With just three buttons and a joystick, controls are easy to pick up but challenging to master</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/500ec4a1aa6198ab5f9b503d1a174678.poster.avif?t=1770091663\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/500ec4a1aa6198ab5f9b503d1a174678.webm?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/500ec4a1aa6198ab5f9b503d1a174678.mp4?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shake Things Up</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your favorite game mode, or play a random one each round</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your perfect rules and settings for maximum fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as individuals or teams, with or without AI bots</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/430d92a608b80c4e08ab5937697d5e68.poster.avif?t=1770091663\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/430d92a608b80c4e08ab5937697d5e68.webm?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127570/extras/430d92a608b80c4e08ab5937697d5e68.mp4?t=1770091663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Super Platform Tag is best enjoyed with controllers when playing with more than one person</h2>",
